            <strong>Safer and more secure</strong>
            <p>Windows 10 provides virus and real-time protection against threats from malicious apps and ransomware. And you get ongoing updates from the cloud, so you'll always be up-to-date to fight the latest threats.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="icon-why-upgrade">
            <div class="img">
